title: The Artie Quitter Podcast JUL 09 2015 Thu.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.
Co-Hosts for Artie include Comedians Joe Matarese, Gino Bisconti, Sue Costello  and Chris Cotton, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.


TODAY's SHOW

Artie, Gino Bisconti & Chris Cotton are Joined by Thursday regulars Stacey Prussman & Mike Bocchetti. 

* Jason Pierre Paul fireworks Audio Dicussions.

*The ongoing MIKE BOCCHETTI passport saga continues.

*Editor-in-Chief/Radio Personality at BuzzNtheBurgh.com JOSH KING calls in to talk about a movie he wrote set to star MIKE BOCCHETTI
